  "templates": [
    {
      "id": "info",
      "label": "Informational chat",
      "subject": "Quick question about {firm}'s {desk} desk",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nI came across your move to {firm} and wanted to reach out. I'm focused on building a career in fixed income sales & trading here in New York, coming from {background}.\n\nI'd value 15 minutes to hear how you think about the desk and where you're seeing the most interesting flow right now. Happy to work entirely around your schedule.\n\nWould a short call in the next couple of weeks work?\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "referral",
      "label": "Ask for referral",
      "subject": "{firm} {desk} \u2014 referral",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nThanks again for taking the time to chat. Our conversation reinforced that {firm}'s desk is exactly the environment I'm aiming for.\n\nI noticed a relevant opening on the {desk} side \u2014 would you be comfortable referring me, or pointing me to the right person on the team? Happy to send whatever makes that easy on your end.\n\nAppreciate it either way.\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "followup",
      "label": "Follow-up nudge",
      "subject": "Following up \u2014 {me}",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nWanted to follow up on my note from last week. I know the desk keeps you busy, so no pressure \u2014 just flagging that I'm still very interested in connecting whenever the timing works.\n\nThanks,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "coffee",
      "label": "Coffee / in-person",
      "subject": "Coffee near {firm}?",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nI'm going to be around midtown over the next couple of weeks and would love to grab a quick coffee if you have 20 minutes. I'm working toward a fixed income S&T seat and would value your read on the market and the desk.\n\nAny morning that works for you?\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "reconnect",
      "label": "Reconnect (old contact)",
      "subject": "Catching up",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nIt's been a while \u2014 hope things are going well at {firm}. I've been focused on moving into fixed income sales & trading and thought of you given your seat on the {desk} side.\n\nWould love to catch up briefly if you're open to it. No agenda beyond hearing how you're seeing things.\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "postapp",
      "label": "After applying",
      "subject": "Application \u2014 {firm} {desk}",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nI recently applied for a role on the {desk} desk at {firm} and wanted to reach out directly. I'd be grateful for any insight into the team or the process \u2014 and if it's appropriate, I'd welcome the chance to put a name to the application.\n\nThanks for considering it.\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "thankyou",
      "label": "Thank-you (post-meeting)",
      "subject": "Thank you",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\nThank you for the time today \u2014 it was genuinely helpful. Your point about {desk} flow gave me a lot to think about, and it reinforced why I'm targeting this space.\n\nI'll keep you posted on how things progress, and please don't hesitate if there's ever anything I can do in return.\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    },
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "label": "Cold intro (mutual contact)",
      "subject": "Intro via {via}",
      "body": "Hi {first},\n\n{via} suggested I reach out. I'm working toward a fixed income S&T role in New York and {via} thought your perspective from the {desk} side at {firm} would be valuable.\n\nWould you have 15 minutes in the coming weeks? Happy to work around your calendar.\n\nBest,\n{me}"
    }
  ],
  "profile": {
    "name": "",
    "background": "a background in fixed income markets"
  }
